---
title: Creamy Tex-Mex Pork Mince Fusilli with Cheddar & Coriander
description: Here’s a cuisine combo we’re excited to try - Mexican and Italian! Pork mince is cooked in a creamy tomato sauce with Tex-Mex
spices, before being tossed through golden twirls of fusili and Cheddar cheese. This meal is sure to be a hit with the whole family!
